This is the ABOUT file.
This file describes this project.

This project is an attempt to craete a simple API framework in php/mysql.

It is possible to use this project to create an API with relatively little
development time.

The steps to create the first API would be:

1. Design and load the database.
2. Create resources, models and DAOs. (scafolding is coming soon)
3. Add created resources to configuration
4. Use, test and tweak the API
